---
title: Pork Piccata with garlic butter sauce and roasted broccoli
description: This pork piccata is a variation of the Italian-American favourite dish chicken piccata. The cooking method allows the pork to become crispy on the outside and tender on the inside. A herby buttery sauce finishes the dish with a flourish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R02_W20_IE_IECLP14861-3_Main_1_high-7df333b2.jpg
